<subSubSection id="5C62DF33244A38C14BE849D24409113D" pageId="12" pageNumber="25" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="889652A01FC485139DF719AC4396B6F0" pageId="12" pageNumber="25">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4F53730DD39032FEF790CA49785542BB" pageId="12" pageNumber="25">We are pleased to name this ant in honor of Dr Jacques Delabie (CPDC) for his contribution to ant taxonomy and biology and his unconditional support for many ant biologists working in the Neotropics.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
